      "text": [
        "2048 - وَ سَأَلَ زُرَارَةُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : عَنْ صَوْمِ اَلدَّهْرِ فَقَالَ «لَمْ يَزَلْ مَكْرُوهاً»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2048 - Zurara asked Abu Abdullah (as) about fasting continuously throughout the year.\nImam (as) replied: \"It has always been disliked.\""
        ]
      }
    }
